        "content": "## 1. Listen for Linear Issue Events\n[Learn more about the Linear Trigger node](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/linear/)\n\nThis node captures events from Linear like issue creation, update, or removal‚Äîit's the starting point of our workflow."
